name: Warung Jepun Tembles
address: Jalan Denpasar Gilimanuk, Negara, Jl. Banjar Tembles, Penyaringan, Kec. Mendoyo, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82261, Indonesia
review 1: The best fried tenggiri & soup tenggiri. Got to try these dishes. Warung Jepun Tembles is serving top quality. Superb.
review 2:
Clean restaurant. Fast service. Excellent taste. We ordered ayam betutu komplit (whole chicken) for IDR 160.000 complete with rice, kangkung, fried peanut & rice.

The price is a bit pricey, but its worth to try.

For those of you who traveled by car, i think its a nice stop to have a lunch break before heading to gilimanuk harbor.
review 3: I found this place by accident, when I was heading to Denpasar. What a great place and ambiance and also friendly staff. However, they need to consider the food taste.
review 4: Finally a clean place with a very high value for money on the way to Denpasar from Gilimanuk. Food also good and fresh.
review 5: a comfortable place to rest while traveling from Gilimanuk to Denpasar. Reasonable food prices. fast and friendly service.

name: RM Anak Minang

review 1: Great location, food ok not the best
review 3: One of good choice padang restaurant during the trip from Gilimanuk harbour to Denpasar...
review 4: Cold food. Not tasty. Dusty place. Not recommendable for western.
review 5: Padang restaurant with beautiful rice field view
